# Otto combined demo — server, PR review with selection, PR lifecycle
Output docs/images/otto-demo.gif
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 880
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 15
Set Shell bash
Set TypingSpeed 0

Hide
Type "bash docs/images/demo-scripts/demo-combined.sh"
Enter
Show

Sleep 35s
